description:
Hi all.

Would like to know how active are all members within this group, as probably was created time ago and some of them might not be even living in Brussels.

I've just bought all my gear and really feel like starting riding in the Netherlands! Therefore, now looking for ppl with the same interest to enjoy together this sport.

Moreover, as a warm up, we could meet for a beer in Brussels to get to know each other and sort out some future kitesurf day trips.

Looking forward your feedbacks!
name: Kitesurf meeting
Kitesurfing this Sunday (13/10) in Netherlands if the wind allows ;)
Another try for this Sunday, 20 Oct, at Baartland, if not cancelled...

description: Hi everyone and welcome to the Brussels KiteSurfers group. As the new season is approaching we would like to meet the new members of the group and see who's new to the sport and get to know each other. We'll discuss about spots, weather conditions, kite gears and equipments, kite schools... and work things out for the kite session. Hope to see you all for the meeting !
name: Kitesurf meeting.

description: Hi everyone, as you all know conditions are very good for kitesurfing sessions. We've had an excellent weather last weekend with many riders for fun and enjoying the day at the beach. If you're interested we can manage a meetup at the beach of Oostvoorne (restaurants, toilets and warm showers available) for those looking for lessons and some of you who want to kitesurf with their own equipment. We can manage carpooling for those of you who don't have a car and a camping is possible for the whole weekend stay. Please let me know how many of you are interested. Hope to meet you soon. Stay tuned !! Anass
name: Kitesurf session this weekend 28-29/06/2014 !

description:
Hi there guys, gals,


I saw that this saturday should be windy in Oostvoorne (netherlands) is anybody in to go there?

PS:
Since I'm beginner I'm gonna take lessons it would be nice to have a small group so I can call the guy and book the lesson.
name: Kitesurfing Oostvoorne!
